{"tid":1447850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"4000蚊個口罩 搶錢咩","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:17:54.000Z","uid":259359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ecb5045c35c021fbf4564ac63d84f66543d78b7","tid":1447850,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/proudtobeHongKongChinese/permalink/2522588207763924?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FproudtobeHongKongChinese%2Fpermalink%2F2522588207763924%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=d7e3e6c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/proudtobeHongKongChinese/permalink/2522588207763924?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n《2019-08-10送上好消息》<br />\n<br />\n已证实在昨天晚上行动中👍由西九龙冲锋队執行的拘捕行动中👍拉到7個pink team (粉紅行动队员)全部是全副整套齐全重裝備。<br />\n粉紅暴徒出战每人每天行动费一万元。<br />\n粉紅戰队是黑曱甴最厉害最有戦鬥力队伍。<br />\n所用武裝是美军海军陆戰队使用的，单是口罩己是四仟港元&mdash;个。<br />\n粉紅戰队是由七至十二人组成&mdash;个攻击小队、帶领曱甴在不同地点和警方戦鬥、前段時间、每次有八至十队參予。但昨天現埸观察所得全程好像只有一至兩队。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4000蚊喎 政府派4000蚊都係買到個口罩咋原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5b7a4699f9c1e8423bb1edc8ae8cdbf2a246d2","tid":1447850,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:22.000Z","msg":"4000呀！"},{"pid":"f02ab511e7bd38a9f708febfc01d7bcdf39e9f65","tid":1447850,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"明明我買既係百幾蚊"},{"pid":"2465db18711843f4be4c94050bfa429df9984e0f","tid":1447850,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"放係枱影又嫁禍既"},{"pid":"7ed1c0fc48bf6fee19c89bede1418e0711798289","tid":1447850,"uid":259359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家<img src=\